### Git status
GET http://localhost:8080/v1/git/status/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000010
x-user-id: 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000100

### Git repo link
GET http://localhost:8080/v1/git/repo-link/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000010
x-user-id: 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000100

### Get git config
GET http://localhost:8080/v1/git/config/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000010
x-user-id: 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000100

### Set git config
PUT http://localhost:8080/v1/git/config/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000010
x-user-id: 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000100
content-type: application/json

{
  "remote_url": "/tmp/typst-remote.git",
  "default_branch": "main"
}

### List personal access tokens
GET http://localhost:8080/v1/security/tokens
x-user-id: 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000100

### Create personal access token
POST http://localhost:8080/v1/security/tokens
x-user-id: 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000100
content-type: application/json

{
  "label": "CLI laptop",
  "expires_at": null
}

